{"word":"ἐμπαίζω","slug":"ἐμπαίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπαίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to mock at, mock</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>illudere</el>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to sport in</i> or <i>on</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}